software that you

00:41:44.780 --> 00:41:47.100
can use to point into
any part of database

00:41:47.100 --> 00:41:49.350
and obtain not a
table as a result,

00:41:49.350 --> 00:41:50.820
but obtain a visualization.

00:41:50.820 --> 00:41:53.075
And then by taking
these visualizations

00:41:53.075 --> 00:41:54.450
and putting them
