00:41:54.450 --> 00:41:56.600
going to start creating stories
that allow you to understand

00:41:56.600 --> 00:41:58.250
the systems that
are being described

00:41:58.250 --> 00:42:01.400
and the information that
is embodied in that data.

00:42:01.400 --> 00:42:02.999
So I'm going to
